OL,6,FA care home worker defrauded an
OL,7,Felderly resident of tens of thousands
OL,8,Fof pounds after he gained the man's
OL,9,Ftrust and took advantage of his
OL,10,Fvulnerability.
OL,12,FNikola Penevski, 35, of Walsh Avenue
OL,13,Fin Hengrove, abused his position as a
OL,14,Fdeputy manager of Rosedale House Care
OL,15,FHome to withdraw more than #40,000
OL,16,Ffrom the resident's bank account.
