OL,6,FHe made dozens of withdrawals between
OL,7,FJanuary 2022 and December of the same
OL,8,Fyear until this activity was flagged
OL,9,Fby the bank. The victim died in March
OL,10,F2023.
OL,12,FPenevski was arrested by Met Police
OL,13,Fofficers at Heathrow Airport in
OL,14,FJanuary 2023 after he returned to the
OL,15,Fcountry from a trip overseas.
OL,17,FHe pleaded guilty to fraud by abuse of
OL,18,Fposition in June and was sentenced to
OL,19,F27 months in prison when he appeared
OL,20,Fat Bristol Crown Court on Wednesday 24
OL,21,FJuly.
