OL,6,FThe investigating officer, DC Daniel
OL,7,FBritton, said: "Penevski was uniquely
OL,8,Fplaced, given his position within the
OL,9,Fcare home, to fraudulently obtain tens
OL,10,Fof thousands of pounds of the victim's
OL,11,Fmoney.
OL,13,F"The victim had come to the home
OL,14,Fbecause he needed additional care, was
OL,15,Fparticularly vulnerable and had no
OL,16,Fsupport network available to him.
OL,17,FPenevski gained his trust and then
OL,18,Fexploited that vulnerability.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
