OL,6,F"Sadly, the victim passed away before
OL,7,FPenevski had acknowledged his
OL,8,Fculpability in this crime.
OL,10,F"I wish to place on record my sincere
OL,11,Fgratitude to the staff and
OL,12,Fparticularly the management, at
OL,13,FRosedale House who have been extremely
OL,14,Fsupportive throughout this
OL,15,Finvestigation.
OL,17,F"Penevski's actions will have resulted
OL,18,Fin a particularly stressful time for
OL,19,Fthem all - and for the other residents.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
